Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 1: I'm going to expedite it for you, so you'll get that by Friday.

Speaker 2: You should get it by Saturday, yeah.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All right.
